175 A.3d 170 ESTATE OF PATRICIA M. QUINN, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. MICHAEL F. QUINN (DECEASED), DEFENDANT. (MARITA QUINN-PETITIONER)

C-327 September Term 2017

079877 November 17, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001490-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
